      <w:r><w:t>1. Payment</w:t></w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:r><w:t>The customer shall pay each undisputed invoice within 30 days of receipt.</w:t></w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="Heading1"/></w:pPr>
      <w:r><w:t>2. Governing Law</w:t></w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:r><w:t>This Agreement shall be governed by the laws of India and the courts at Bengaluru shall have jurisdiction.</w:t></w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="Heading1"/></w:pPr>
      <w:r><w:t>3. Miscellaneous</w:t></w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:r><w:t>If any provision of this Agreement is held invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall remain in full force and effect.</w:t></w:r>
    </w:p>
